â”œâ”€â”€ Economic Analysis (Resource flows, corporate roles)
â”œâ”€â”€ Gender/Class Analysis (Women's roles, labor history)
â””â”€â”€ Ecological Impact (Environmental consequences)
```

Mechanism: AI-DN aggregates all available sourcesâ€”diaries, oral histories, satellite imagery (where applicable), economic data, even climate recordsâ€”and presents them as interconnected layers.

2. The Validation Protocol: Consensus Through Disagreement

Step 1: Source Authentication

Â· Every historical claim requires verification chains
Â· AI-DN traces claims back to original sources
Â· Digital signatures for modern accounts, provenance analysis for ancient ones

